│ beginning of the\n    // phi-block. We have to make sure     │
│ that the chained vectors are computed\n    // before the new │
│ PHI.\n    BasicBlock *PHParent = PH->getParent();\n          │
│ Builder.SetInsertPoint(PHParent->getFirstNonPHI());\n```\n\n │
│ **File**:                                                    │
│ `llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp`\n\n```cpp\ │
│ n// llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp:5193\n   │
│ Value *V = vectorizeOperand(PH, I);\n                        │
│ NewPHI->addIncoming(V, PH->getIncomingBlock(I));\n           │
│ }\n```\n\n**Edit Point 2**:                                  │
│ `llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp` from line  │
│ 5193 to 5193.\n\n```cpp\n//                                  │
│ llvm/lib/Transforms/Vectorize/SLPVectorizer.cpp:5193\n       │
│ BasicBlock *IncomingBB = PH->getIncomingBlock(I);\n          │
